{"tid":634463,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"呢到有冇人成功申請獎學金","createTime":"2018-04-19T08:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T17:56:41.000Z","uid":72593,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5335e98c0c8acaddcd2ec8675f9be4fb3dae3f52","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"小弟最近成功申請到一個叫外展體驗奬(roa)既scholarship 目的係岀外地睇一個關於本科既展覽 有少少野想問<br />\n1.如果例如展覽為期六日 我去一日佢個獎學金係咪都會批足？<br />\n2.咁六日展 但我plan個trip係去9日又得唔得？<br />\n3.可以claim一皮 但如果個trip只洗咗7千又可唔可以claim足哂？<br />\n<br />\n跪求成功人士/以往曾經申請既師兄師姐回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ea2d1c1ac1b7acf366e6ef9a1ab89afdb0dadb","tid":634463,"uid":1400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"用7k claim 10k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e678893430c378421339595a7837cf45e684631","tid":634463,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5335e98c0c8acaddcd2ec8675f9be4fb3dae3f52","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"小弟最近成功申請到一個叫外展體驗奬(roa)既scholarship 目的係岀外地睇一個關於本科既展覽 有少少野想問<br />\n1.如果例如展覽為期六日 我去一日佢個獎學金係咪都會批足？<br />\n2.咁六日展 但我plan個trip係去9日又得唔得？<br />\n3.可以claim一皮 但如果個trip只洗咗7千又可唔可以claim足哂？<br />\n<br />\n跪求成功人士/以往曾經申請既師兄師姐回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"無申請過呢個獎學金但申請過去外地開conference既travel grant 或者可以參考<br />\n我既經驗係：<br />\n去一日就應該得一日或兩日一夜錢<br />\n你去幾多日佢應該唔理 佢只俾一至兩日錢你<br />\nclaim既錢係計economy class機票錢同埋一晚酒店錢(佢應該有specify係幾星級) 唔夠數就無得claim盡<br />\n<br />\n但唔知你個獎係咪一樣具體要求，所以你打去問清楚佢就最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab92d3d2a6e49e95b3c94416f5619d768257f99","tid":634463,"uid":47177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"用100蚊都可以claim足10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bd5ea4a83a210f94a9db8879cb4388ba07bccd","tid":634463,"uid":123031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"可以 <br />\n利申： 成功者"},{"pid":"250f49a3c76fd02f98715083a371515ce87d0a9a","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用7k claim 10k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盡用資源嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願食少兩餐都想claim多少少補貼學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01773895903d6e6dec929026f51dbb45a98f6be5","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟最近成功申請到一個叫外展體驗奬(roa)既scholarship 目的係岀外地睇一個關於本科既展覽 有少少野想問<br />\n1.如果例如展覽為期六日 我去一日佢個獎學金係咪都會批足？<br />\n2.咁六日展 但我plan個trip係去9日又得唔得？<br />\n3.可以claim一皮 但如果個trip只洗咗7千又可唔可以claim足哂？<br />\n<br />\n跪求成功人士/以往曾經申請既師兄師姐回答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>無申請過呢個獎學金但申請過去外地開conference既travel grant 或者可以參考<br />\n我既經驗係：<br />\n去一日就應該得一日或兩日一夜錢<br />\n你去幾多日佢應該唔理 佢只俾一至兩日錢你<br />\nclaim既錢係計economy class機票錢同埋一晚酒店錢(佢應該有specify係幾星級) 唔夠數就無得claim盡<br />\n<br />\n但唔知你個獎係咪一樣具體要求，所以你打去問清楚佢就最穩陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該師兄 佢冇講要坐咩class或者幾星酒店 我過排再打去詳細問 anyway thanks ching"},{"pid":"a32dd944b1d871a0133bc66ef12028aa3e3e2863","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以 <br />\n利申： 成功者</blockquote><br />\n師兄有冇多少少detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果六日展 去一日only 我怕佢到時問返 點解唔去多幾日/去足六日 或者你去九日點解淨係去一日個展覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2603658e2e10fa3b9cc3fa0fb04d99fc19431d","tid":634463,"uid":109538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"好似佢會要你計報價先架，<br />\n你報大過一皮嘢，佢就俾足你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31214ea7aaae8a82d31100ffc838e644143ecb88","tid":634463,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"邊間u先？"},{"pid":"a5a04d1c5485eda5f11ebfb17be6c24c0c517a7a","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間u先？</blockquote><br />\n唔答 怕自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb43cb788bbce33959cf42a99b9c56b9f60d66c","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T19:44:45.000Z","msg":"莫非呢個獎冇一個萬能連登仔中過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以解答吓問題1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d901fbdfc2dc29f7866870e51c7f8aebb5b82717","tid":634463,"uid":76751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T19:55:05.000Z","msg":"用5k claim 10k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ce12c54bb4f1542f040f83739af31cf58ebcac","tid":634463,"uid":31646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T20:10:20.000Z","msg":"1. 你唔比人周到應該ok<br />\n2. 你自己去玩 都係唔比人周到應該ok<br />\n3. 10k<br />\n利申 3k claim 10k"},{"pid":"231f6bcf8ea02351457d0d425b8e87ab0f27bb44","tid":634463,"uid":123031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a32dd944b1d871a0133bc66ef12028aa3e3e2863","tid":634463,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以 <br />\n利申： 成功者</blockquote><br />\n師兄有冇多少少detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果六日展 去一日only 我怕佢到時問返 點解唔去多幾日/去足六日 或者你去九日點解淨係去一日個展覽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"我個陣寫個proposal 去台灣體驗生態文化乜乜乜<br />\n之後去到台灣拎一日遊for呢個ROA 去個d乜鬼中正紀念堂個d野 不過你記得要keep機票 車票 除左食同shopping既單外 都要夾俾佢做references<br />\n個時玩左5日4夜 洗4-5千 但記寫用九千幾<br />\n因為佢之後會問你住同車費 大概會用幾多<br />\n咁個陣都係吹水 每個作大佢 <br />\n<br />\n祝你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}